svg.text: Photo Processing Tool: Make Your Photos Look BeautifulTrue, ugly, if the photo is skewed, like a portrait sadly hanging on a nail? If you tilted the camera too much when you took the picture, or placed the photo slightly in the scanner, use the rotation function to align any photo.On the Ediring platform, time is not spent on drawing: rotation effects are displayed in real time on all sections of the design so that the image is smooth and beautiful.
